headline: Quest Diagnostics to Improve Laboratory Testing Experience with Industry-First Epic Collaboration
summary: Quest Diagnostics (NYSE: DGX) and Epic today announced a first-of-its-kind collaboration designed to streamline and improve experiences for healthcare providers and patients that engage Quest for laboratory testing in the United States.
